<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Provider Registration Received</h1>
  
  <p>Dear <%= @registration.provider_name %>,</p>
  
  <p>Thank you for submitting your provider registration to Autism Services Locator. We have received your application and will review it shortly.</p>
  
  <h2>Registration Details:</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Provider Name:</strong> <%= @registration.provider_name %></li>
    <li><strong>Category:</strong> <%= @registration.category_display_name %></li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @registration.email %></li>
    <li><strong>Submitted:</strong> <%= @registration.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
  </ul>
  
  <h2>What Happens Next?</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Our team will review your registration information</li>
    <li>We may contact you for additional details if needed</li>
    <li>You will receive an email notification once your registration is approved or rejected</li>
    <li>If approved, your provider information will be added to our directory</li>
  </ol>
  
  <p>This process typically takes 2-3 business days. If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The Autism Services Locator Team</p>
</body>
</html> 